OL,7,FRushdie did not attend the sentencing
OL,8,Fat the court in western New York but
OL,9,Fsubmitted a victim impact statement.
OL,11,FThe 77-year-old author testified
OL,12,Fduring the trial, telling jurors he
OL,13,Fthought he was dying as a masked man
OL,14,Fstabbed him more than a dozen times in
OL,15,Fthe head and torso while he was being
OL,16,Fintroduced at the Chautauqua
OL,17,FInstitution, where he was due to speak
OL,18,Fabout protecting writers.
