OL,7,FBefore being sentenced, Matar stood
OL,8,Fand made a statement about freedom of
OL,9,Fspeech, calling Rushdie a hypocrite.
OL,11,F"Salman Rushdie wants to disrespect
OL,12,Fother people," Matar said, dressed in
OL,13,Fwhite-striped jail clothing and
OL,14,Fwearing handcuffs. "He wants to be a
OL,15,Fbully, he wants to bully other people.
OL,16,FI don't agree with that."
