OL,7,F"Every day since then, for the last
OL,8,Fcouple of years, this case has been an
OL,9,Finternational publicity sponge," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"There was no presumption, ever, of
OL,13,Finnocence for Mr Matar from the very
OL,14,Fbeginning."
OL,16,FRushdie spent 17 days in a
OL,17,FPennsylvania hospital and more than
OL,18,Fthree weeks recovering at a
OL,19,Frehabilitation centre in New York
OL,20,FCity. He detailed his recovery in his
OL,21,F2024 memoir, Knife.
