OL,7,FMatar now faces a federal trial on
OL,8,Fterrorism-related charges. While the
OL,9,Ffirst trial focused on the stabbing
OL,10,Fitself, the next is expected to
OL,11,Fexplore his motives.
OL,13,FProsecutors say Matar, a US citizen,
OL,14,Ftravelled from his home in Fairview,
OL,15,FNew Jersey, to carry out a decades-old
OL,16,Ffatwa, or edict, calling for Rushdie's
OL,17,Fdeath.
