OL,7,FThough Iran later said it would no
OL,8,Flonger enforce the fatwa, and Rushdie
OL,9,Fhad lived relatively freely in recent
OL,10,Fdecades, Matar believed it remained
OL,11,Fvalid.
OL,13,FFederal prosecutors say he viewed the
OL,14,Ffatwa as endorsed by Hezbollah, citing
OL,15,Fa 2006 speech by the group's leader,
OL,16,FHassan Nasrallah.
